=C2=A0

Up top, you=E2=80=99ll also
find intel from me on another Proenza Schouler bombshell=E2=80=94the Proenz=
a boys are stepping down from Proenza=E2=80=94plus, all you need to know ab=
out the GQ=E2=80=93Super Bowl fashion-show thingy. Meanwhile, Sarah Shapiro=
 explains why the heck G-III, owner of Donna Karan International and Karl L=
agerfeld, invested in this new Saks-Neiman entity.

Before we get started, a little note from Los Angeles: One of the great thi=
ngs about moving
