Why is Charlotte Tilbury=E2=80=94both the brand and its famous founder=E2=
=80=94so
upset about the latest iteration of the dupe market? It=E2=80=99s a pain in=
 the neck, sure, but fans contend that it=E2=80=99s democratizing the beaut=
y counter. Either way, Charlotte=E2=80=99s battle is a sign of some larger =
challenges to come.=C2=A0

Rachel Strugatz ( https://puck.news/author/rachel-strugatz/?utm_campaign=3D=
Line+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%281%2F15%2F25%29&utm_content=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSC=
RIBERS+%281%2F15%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io=
&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a )
Rachel Strugatz ( https://puck.news/author/rachel-strugatz/?utm_campaign=3D=
Line+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%281%2F15%2F25%29&utm_content=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSC=
